Package: nepa.project
Title: Sector-level NEPA Exposure Measure (Phi_i)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jackson", "Mejia", email = "jmejia@americafirstpolicy.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Replicable construction of a per-sector NEPA review exposure
    measure from EPA EIS data (Federal Register API) and BEA fixed-asset data.
    Companion code for the AFPI working paper on aggregate effects of NEPA reform.
